\begin_layout Section
Conclusion
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
We were able to find significant differences according to a t-test method
 that is commonly used for microarray experiments in ChIP-seq data.
 Our statistics might be underpowered because we do not have a good model
 fit but it's possible that better improvements would find a better solution.
 We considered other software including edgeR, a negative binomial test
 that is a successor or limma for HTS data and DIME, a mixture model for
 differential expression for ChIP-seq specifically.
 
